snippet.textDisplay: Is it me, or has 10 Minute Power Hour gotten more and more uninteresting/entertaining over time? Bobbing for apples? Come one guys...it also seems that whomever is putting these things together puts very little thought into the actual production of the video. If they're supposed to not be able to see, why the hell wouldn't they provide them blindfolds...at the very least. It legitimately seems as if they just think of an idea and do the bare minimum to put that idea on video.  I find myself skipping 10 Minute Power Hour more and more. This is boring and uninspired even though Arin and Dan always try to make the best out of these videos. Not that my word means anything, but come on folks, try a little harder.
